<p rend="chapter">2. Akusalapeyyālaṃ</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="191-200"><hi rend="paranum">191-200</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi><hi rend="bold">Sāvajjā</hi>ti <pb ed="V" n="2.0067" /> sadosā. <hi rend="bold">Anavajjā</hi>ti niddosā. <hi rend="bold">Dukkhudrayā</hi>ti dukkhavaḍḍhikā. <hi rend="bold">Sukhudriyā</hi>ti sukhavaḍḍhikā. <hi rend="bold">Sabyābajjhā</hi>ti sadukkhā. <hi rend="bold">Abyābajjhā</hi>ti niddukkhā. Ettāvatā vaṭṭavivaṭṭameva kathitaṃ.</p>

<p rend="centre">Akusalapeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.</p>
